# Naming Conventions

Use **camelCase** for all file and directory names. Do not use dashes (kebab-case) or underscores (snake_case).

```
# ✅ Good
useSignOut.ts
useStore.ts
exampleForm.tsx
authHelpers.ts

# ❌ Bad
use-sign-out.ts
use-store.ts
example-form.tsx
auth-helpers.ts
```

Exceptions:
- Next.js route files that must follow framework conventions (`page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `loading.tsx`, etc.)
- Config files at the project root (`tailwind.config.ts`, `next.config.ts`, etc.)
- Component files may use PascalCase (`GoogleLoginButton.tsx`, `SignUpForm.tsx`)
